      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PHOENIX AMELIA (1) broke a string of placings finishing in the money three on end before a last start fourth (26.32) at Murray Bridge. Has never missed the frame at the trip from five starts. The form out of last race has been strong. Should be very hard to beat this time. FLYING SEAL (2) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing third and beaten 2 lengths (16.85) behind Amazing Miley at Q Straight. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from seven starts. Expected to feature. MY LOVELY (3) could manage only third at this track last time but turned heads when posting an outstanding 21.59 over 390m at this track three starts ago. Expected to feature on best figures. SPRING RORY (6) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
